<TD><INPUT TYPE="Text" NAME="Title" SIZE="40" value="Part 1: Enter Crimson (Gav, this is a spin-off, an ...(truncated)"></TD>
<TR>
<TD ALIGN="RIGHT" VALIGN="MIDDLE" NOWRAP WIDTH="20%"><FONT SIZE=2>
